      "id": 1,
      "name": "Lt C.Jones",
      "faction": "SI-9",
      "class": "Support",

      "story_short": "At 25, Lt. Catherine Jones was a rising star in SI-9’s technical support unit — loyal, precise, and still clinging to the belief she was fighting for humanity’s good. That changed on her last mission. Her team stormed a dictator’s palace on a distant colony, tasked with eliminating him and his bloodline. ",
      "story_long": "At 25, Lt. Catherine Jones was a rising star in SI-9’s technical support unit — loyal, precise, and still clinging to the belief she was fighting for humanity’s good. That changed on her last mission. Her team stormed a dictator’s palace on a distant colony, tasked with eliminating him and his bloodline. A moment of hesitation from her commander cost them two teammates. Catherine didn’t flinch — she pulled the trigger and ended the mission with a perfect shot to the dictator’s head. Her actions earned top marks and praise from command. But it broke something inside. Sent to a resort planet for psychological recovery, she was blindsided when recalled early for the temple operation. No time to rest. No time to heal. Orders are orders — and Catherine always follows through.",

